#: ../../M/mainsleaze.rst:5
msgid "mainsleaze"
msgstr "mainsleaze"

#: ../../M/mainsleaze.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../M/mainsleaze.rst:10
msgid ""
"Spam emitted by a reputable, mainstream company (as opposed to fly-by-night "
"Viagra oeddlers and the like). Sometime this happens in honest ignorance, "
"but the reputation danage can take years to live down."
msgstr ""
"評判の良い主流の会社が放つspam(夜逃げ同然のViagra売りなどとは対照的に)。これは時に正直な無知から起きるが、評判の損傷は払拭するのに何年もかかりうる。"

#: ../../M/mainsleaze.rst:14
msgid ""
"Occasionally used for a big-time spammer, with its own :ref:`fat-pipe`\\, "
"their own mailservers, and a :ref:`pink-contract`\\. Almost impossible to "
"get shut down."
msgstr ""
"時に、自前の\\ :ref:`fat-pipe`\\ 、自前のメールサーバー、そして\\ :ref:`pink-contract`\\ "
"を持つ大物のスパマーを指すのに使われる。閉鎖させるのはほとんど不可能である。"
